{"id":642752,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/小强蜀熟-新说唱规定，选手不能编脏辫、不能染/","date":"2020-04-28T23:54:00Z","modified":"2020-04-29T00:13:05Z","title":"小强蜀熟 | 新说唱规定，选手不能编脏辫、不能染发","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642753\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-58.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"213\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-58.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-58-300x128.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-58-1024x435.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-58-768x326.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>说唱圈开学了。</p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>今年新说唱将于6月录制，选手将于5月17日抵达无锡，进行14天的隔离，此外在着装方面，选手不能编脏辫、不能染发。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642754\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/2-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1063\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/2-2.png 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/2-2-141x300.png 141w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>也就是说，无论选手风格是old school还是new school，着装上都必须符合school标准——最近全国各地陆续开学复课，说唱圈也不例外。</p>\n<p>（此处应插入说唱圈校歌作为BMG）</p>\n<p>不能编脏辫的规定早已有之，这项规定作用于男性，新说唱的规定写的是“男士不能编脏辫”，没有说女性不能编脏辫。举个最近的例子，在《歌手》总决赛上，袁娅维、马思唯都有脏辫，但马思唯用帽子遮住了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642755\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/3-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/3-11.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/3-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/3-11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/3-11-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在《脱口秀大会》上，臧鸿飞用巨大的帽子裹住脏辫。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642756\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4-300x156.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4-1024x534.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4-768x400.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>池子曾发微博称，梦见节目导演对他说不用戴帽子了，他特别开心。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642757\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5-3.png 865w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5-3-300x90.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5-3-768x231.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>但梦归梦，现实归现实，录节目还是得戴帽子。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642758\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/6-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"236\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/6-1.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/6-1-300x142.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/6-1-1024x484.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/6-1-768x363.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>池子的辫子被湖南广电点名批评过，当时被批评的还有大张伟、李诞，因为染发。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642759\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"652\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7.png 688w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/7-230x300.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" />2017年5月12日的《天天向上》里，大张伟的头发是绿色。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642760\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/8-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/8-1.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/8-1-300x169.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/8-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/8-1-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>李诞头发是粉红色，池子有辫子。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642761\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/9-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/9-1.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/9-1-300x169.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/9-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/9-1-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>被点名批评后， 大张伟把头发染黑了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642762\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/10-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"173\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/10-1.png 861w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/10-1-300x104.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/10-1-768x266.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>除了脏辫、发色，综艺节目还有男性不能戴耳钉（戴了会被打码）、不能纹身（有纹身自行遮住）的不成文规定。</p>\n<p>着装上的规定容易对付，脏辫可以拆、头发可以染黑，或戴帽子遮住，耳钉可以摘，纹身可以遮，这些都不成问题，而最为致命的是，歌词的审核与修改。</p>\n<p>新说唱有个大家熟知的案例是，“C-BLOCK的C是shout out to我的祖国”被改成“楚国”，这又不是在骂祖国，明明是句正能量的歌词，仍然为了规避审查，被迫修改。</p>\n<p>去年8月30日，功夫胖个人巡演至大本营长沙，刘聪对台下观众说：“节目里看到那些东西，那根本就不是我。我想唱的歌只有在这里才能听到，如果你们愿意的话，你们去听那些改词版、剪辑版，歌词整版整版都在改。”</p>\n<p>不光是“楚国”，刘聪被改的歌词太多了，以《天命之军》为例——</p>\n<p>“我借给哥们的钱够你一年工资”改成“我给我哥们的爱够你一年工资”。（炫富）</p>\n<p>“早金盆洗手”改成“早浪子回头”。（金盆洗手常指黑帮改邪归正）</p>\n<p>在台面祭奠你”改成“在台面纪念你”。（祭奠与死亡有关，看本文开头那张图，衣服上不能有与死亡有关的字。综艺里跟死有关的字词，一律加引号）</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642763\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/11-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/11-3.jpg 754w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/11-3-300x192.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>“江山 易改 本性 难移”改成“我行 我素 本性 难移”。（什么？你要改江山？给我抓走！）</p>\n<p>“你把感情当身体需要”改成“你把感情当一种需要”。（身体需要涉黄）</p>\n<p>在歌词审核上，今年新说唱依然会延续去年的严格。在今年的《歌手》上，也可以看到歌词审核的魔幻之处。</p>\n<p>“再给我一支烟”改成“再给我一只眼”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642764\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/12.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/12.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/12-300x169.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/12-1024x576.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/12-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><br />\n“谁都应该被宠爱纹身”改成“谁都应该被宠爱闻声”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642765\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/13-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"241\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/13-1.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/13-1-300x144.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/13-1-1024x493.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/13-1-768x370.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在今年《青春有你》里，《易燃易爆炸》的“盼我疯魔”改为“盼我疯狂”，“轻佻又下贱”改为“轻狂又随便”，“杀人不眨眼”改为“冷面不眨眼”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642766\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/15-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/15-1.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/15-1-300x169.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/15-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/15-1-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>歌词是说唱的灵魂，但为了成名，为了赚钱，有时不得不做出妥协、让步，没办法，大环境就是这样。</p>\n<p>最后，分享一个我认为最魔幻的歌词修改案例。</p>\n<p>《野狼disco》一夜成名后，“这是最好的时代，这是最坏的时代”改成了——</p>\n<p>“这是最好的时代，这是最爱的时代”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-642767\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/16-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/16-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/16-1-300x119.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/16-1-1024x407.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/16-1-768x305.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a class=\"st_tag internal_tag\" title=\"Posts tagged with CDS档案\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/cds%e6%a1%a3%e6%a1%88/\" rel=\"tag\">CDS档案</a> | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6\">审查制度</a></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"FsNUPWfPQX\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/%e8%9d%89%e5%88%9b%e6%84%8f-%e7%9c%9f%e6%b2%a1%e6%83%b3%e5%88%b0%ef%bc%8c%e5%b0%b1%e8%bf%99%e7%82%b9%e5%b0%ba%e5%ba%a6%e4%b9%9f%e8%a6%81%e6%89%93%e7%a0%81%ef%bc%9f%ef%bc%9f%ef%bc%9f/\">蝉创意 | “真没想到，就这点尺度也要打码？？？”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《蝉创意 | “真没想到，就这点尺度也要打码？？？”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/%e8%9d%89%e5%88%9b%e6%84%8f-%e7%9c%9f%e6%b2%a1%e6%83%b3%e5%88%b0%ef%bc%8c%e5%b0%b1%e8%bf%99%e7%82%b9%e5%b0%ba%e5%ba%a6%e4%b9%9f%e8%a6%81%e6%89%93%e7%a0%81%ef%bc%9f%ef%bc%9f%ef%bc%9f/embed/#?secret=FsNUPWfPQX\" data-secret=\"FsNUPWfPQX\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"ufZ0SpXEv3\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/%e5%be%b7%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0-%e9%95%bf%e5%b9%b3%e8%a7%82%e5%af%9f%ef%bc%9a%e6%88%91%e7%9a%84%e5%9b%bd%e5%ae%b6%e6%9c%89%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88-%e7%ac%bc%e7%9a%84%e4%bc%a0/\">德国之声 | 长平观察：我的国家有什么——笼的传人</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《德国之声 | 长平观察：我的国家有什么——笼的传人》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/%e5%be%b7%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0-%e9%95%bf%e5%b9%b3%e8%a7%82%e5%af%9f%ef%bc%9a%e6%88%91%e7%9a%84%e5%9b%bd%e5%ae%b6%e6%9c%89%e4%bb%80%e4%b9%88-%e7%ac%bc%e7%9a%84%e4%bc%a0/embed/#?secret=ufZ0SpXEv3\" data-secret=\"ufZ0SpXEv3\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":997,"categories":[18271,38912,15868,38919],"tags":[18705,21522,40230,40000,10768]}